snippet.title: An Attorney Talks Depp v. Heard, Marilyn Manson, Meghan Markle, and More
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp / Amber Heard / Marilyn Manson / Meghan Markle / Prince Harry / Celebrity Controversies / Legal Analysis 

I talked with criminal defense attorney Andrea Burkhart again about a range of celebrity cases and controversies, including the Johnny Depp/Amber Heard lawsuit, the Marilyn Manson allegations, and Andrea's controversial take on Meghan Markle and the royal family. 

We begin by discussing Depp, then get into her thoughts on the Manson situation, then end with a long discussion of Meghan Markle and the royal family. 

Go to my channel for more great videos, including my earlier interview with Andrea.  I cover celebrity controversies with a deeper philosophical twist.
